{"type":null,"faqId":32945,"title":"拍照支持微距么？拍照和录像过程中是否支持自动对焦、是否支持手动对焦？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>能够支持8cm微距拍摄。拍照过程中可以支持自动对焦和手动对焦。但录像过程中是不能自动对焦的，但可以手动对焦。原因如下：如果录像过程中开启自动对焦，那么对焦过程会也会被录像记录下来，一旦用户移动场景就会触发对焦动作，用户会发现录像画面是来回变动的，使得录像效果不清晰。作为补偿策略，我们支持手动触摸对焦，如果用户感受到录像画面不清楚了，可以在录像过程中通过触摸屏幕手动进行对焦。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7547","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748459000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":43,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"拍照,对焦,换个位置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}